message.body: Hey! So jut reminding you we are going to need I meet up after the main session today
for sure! i've got my stuff with me so i can meet at y'all's cars or wherever.
Ok, if you would like we can meet up before hand and get your stuff in our car so that we don't need to try and meet up after when everyone is leaving.
whatever you prefer, just tell me when/where to be! :D
Yea where did you guys park?
we're in the red deck but i have my stuff with me in my community group so i don't really need to go back to the car.
Oh gotcha! Ok well if you want I can pull up the van and you can put it in, or if you don't mind carrying it with you we can meet up at the Starbucks in
building C. That might be easier... Do either of those work for you? :)
starbucks is fine. after group or after the session?
After the session, if that works...
perfect. just making sure. see you then!
